{"tid":2383518,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國泰擬發行67.4億元可換股債券應對疫情挑戰","createTime":"2021-01-28T03:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T08:08:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"54b95f62f5c3180793f09c0d9a92c543c3a2c9be","tid":2383518,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:07:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572751-20210128.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572751-20210128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU0ZHjOsADYkIOf4eYSwfwZo%3D&h=65a7217f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572751-20210128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=28a93c17\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572751-20210128.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n國泰航空建議發行67.4億元5年期有擔保可換股債券，集資所得將用於一般公司用途。國泰說，發行債券可進一步加強集團流動性及充實營運資金，有效應對新型肺炎疫情帶來的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n債券年期5年，息率2.75%，每半年派息一次。初步轉換價每股8.57元，較昨日收市溢價30%。假設以每股8.57元悉數換股，債券將轉換為超過7.86億股新股，相當於擴大後已發行股本約10.89%。"},{"pid":"093a17b138d25ddc11dd2f911d3a44cbbdf75560","tid":2383518,"uid":50502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"然後直接倒閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402457381c7c087335962e652c1601d2b52d6bd7","tid":2383518,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:18:48.000Z","msg":"留名等睇IFC 排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266a644c05c04388ad75345075804699393570bb","tid":2383518,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T03:19:10.000Z","msg":"直插到一蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dbd675daef36509280f3e701949f37b8d49352e","tid":2383518,"uid":70786,"like":